  "detailed_description": "Cardlike is a combination of a traditional roguelike and a card game. Pick one of the three different classes, build your deck, find powerful items, destroy your enemies and try to defeat all five bosses across four unique biomes. Try it out and see how far you can go into the randomly generated dungeon before you!<br><br>Attack your opponents by using cards you collected!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/3ab0a48b4165c5fae3f9ebb6987a96fb.poster.avif?t=1668725275\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/3ab0a48b4165c5fae3f9ebb6987a96fb.webm?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/3ab0a48b4165c5fae3f9ebb6987a96fb.mp4?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you dive deeper into the dungeon build your deck along the way!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/4b3f8eaf80fa8f1b144f387babe0bd5b.poster.avif?t=1668725275\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/4b3f8eaf80fa8f1b144f387babe0bd5b.webm?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/4b3f8eaf80fa8f1b144f387babe0bd5b.mp4?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play as one of the 3 unique characters with completely different playstyles and abilities<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/9c3cf27615c1302cca258e336de041d5.poster.avif?t=1668725275\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/9c3cf27615c1302cca258e336de041d5.webm?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/9c3cf27615c1302cca258e336de041d5.mp4?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Randomly generated dungeons make every run fun and special!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/36ed25601bc9a8c9131a559e53951b9b.poster.avif?t=1668725275\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/36ed25601bc9a8c9131a559e53951b9b.webm?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/36ed25601bc9a8c9131a559e53951b9b.mp4?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game may be difficult, but it's fair.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/74bfda92eb389b57fd5bf5b8c79de9a6.poster.avif?t=1668725275\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/74bfda92eb389b57fd5bf5b8c79de9a6.webm?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/74bfda92eb389b57fd5bf5b8c79de9a6.mp4?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Cardlike is a combination of a traditional roguelike and a card game. Pick one of the three different classes, build your deck, find powerful items, destroy your enemies and try to defeat all five bosses across four unique biomes. Try it out and see how far you can go into the randomly generated dungeon before you!<br><br>Attack your opponents by using cards you collected!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/3ab0a48b4165c5fae3f9ebb6987a96fb.poster.avif?t=1668725275\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/3ab0a48b4165c5fae3f9ebb6987a96fb.webm?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/3ab0a48b4165c5fae3f9ebb6987a96fb.mp4?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you dive deeper into the dungeon build your deck along the way!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/4b3f8eaf80fa8f1b144f387babe0bd5b.poster.avif?t=1668725275\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/4b3f8eaf80fa8f1b144f387babe0bd5b.webm?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/4b3f8eaf80fa8f1b144f387babe0bd5b.mp4?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play as one of the 3 unique characters with completely different playstyles and abilities<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/9c3cf27615c1302cca258e336de041d5.poster.avif?t=1668725275\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/9c3cf27615c1302cca258e336de041d5.webm?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/9c3cf27615c1302cca258e336de041d5.mp4?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Randomly generated dungeons make every run fun and special!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/36ed25601bc9a8c9131a559e53951b9b.poster.avif?t=1668725275\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/36ed25601bc9a8c9131a559e53951b9b.webm?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/36ed25601bc9a8c9131a559e53951b9b.mp4?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game may be difficult, but it's fair.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/74bfda92eb389b57fd5bf5b8c79de9a6.poster.avif?t=1668725275\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/74bfda92eb389b57fd5bf5b8c79de9a6.webm?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580500/extras/74bfda92eb389b57fd5bf5b8c79de9a6.mp4?t=1668725275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
